<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(د)</span> ,<span class="c5"> وَعَنْ وَهْبِ بْنِ مُنَبِّهٍ قَالَ:</span> سَأَلْتُ جَابِرًا - رضي الله عنه -: هَلْ غَنِمُوا يَوْمَ الْفَتْحِ شَيْئًا؟ ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> لَا. <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
